        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25144711/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25144711/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/40470092/" class=" " title="小丑">小丑</a>
                (Everything can be simple)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25144711">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">每当我失去一只臂膀，就获得了一只眼睛</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-14 15:59</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                每当我失去一只臂膀，就获得了一只眼睛
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







